Title: Series: Life of the Virgin after Dürer
Description: The flight into Egypt; Mary rides side-saddle on a donkey led by the reins by Joseph, walking to left, with a walking stick on his shoulder; the travellers, accompanied by a cow, pass a forest of trees; roundel; copy after Dürer (B.VII.132.89; Schoch II.179) Engraving
Bibliographic references: Hollstein / Dutch and Flemish etchings, engravings and woodcuts c.1450-1700 (5) (XIII, p.71)
Acquisition notes: For the probable provenance from Sir Hans Sloane, see the comment on D,5.1.
